Another top spot earned in mobile banking for CIBC
CIBC topped the Forrester 2017 Canadian Mobile Banking Benchmark report. We earned the highest score in mobile banking functionality and usability among Canada’s 5 largest retail banks.1 We also earned the best usability score worldwide in Forrester’s global benchmark. Try our apps for yourself and see what all the fuss is about.
