Need help in an emergency?








1 

















Lost, stolen or damaged card
Call CIBC Credit Card Services – Loss Prevention immediately.
Available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week:
1-800-663-4575
(Canada and the U.S.)
1-514-861-9898
(Elsewhere)








2 

















Travel emergency
Call CIBC Travel Assistance:
1-800-848-8454
(Canada and the U.S.)
Call collect 
1-416-340-7124
(Elsewhere)
Get travel insurance








3 

















Suspicious activity
Think someone else has accessed your account? Tell us immediately. 
Report it by email
Call us: 
1-800-465-2422 
(Canada and the U.S.)
1-902-420-2422 
(Elsewhere)
























