About CIBC


We're celebrating in 2017!
In 2017, we celebrate CIBC’s 150th birthday alongside the 150th anniversary of Canada’s Confederation. We share a history with this beautiful country and are proud to have helped Canadians and businesses prosper over the years. Our commitment to CIBC’s values of Trust, Teamwork and Accountability drives us to create value for our clients, employees, shareholders and our communities.
Learn more


















